  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The experience of the chronic illness negatively engraves on the quality of life of patients.
      Endometriosis is a disease that affects millions of women of childbearing age; it has
      repercussions on psychological health, as shown by numerous recent studies.

      The aim of the present study is to validate the italian version of EPH 30, a self reported
      questionnaire, already used internationally, in order to determine the quality of life in
      women with endometriosis, assess their psychological health and the effectiveness of
      therapies.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
